{"tid":2450064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴　呃鳩我十皮仍不休","createTime":"2021-03-17T06:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:24:41.000Z","uid":343520,"like":76,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e9f553a3d624aafa1f1ed6ca9f807d122550d5","tid":2450064,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴　呃鳩我十皮仍不休<br />\n近日舊同事說你已　飛歐洲抗爭十數週<br />\n攬走錢　聲稱要制裁全香港<br />\n但事實如若倡議要用八皮嘢<br />\n有證據解釋經費嗎？似乎沒有<br />\n<br />\n被打因為共產黨？　誰人會信　是弱智嘛？<br />\n如果要派人威脅你　你其實應該死了啦<br />\n<br />\n那熱民時光　不用常回看<br />\n能成功參與永續Basic Law　就不必再參選<br />\n這熱民時光　未必地老天荒<br />\n陳云根錦滿太念念才難忘<br />\n期望議席留十年　最難是放<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=ba03b371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/</a>　魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"b9c845a97836e195b4f34191a1b84fe20ea5e062","tid":2450064,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5014ce1a3aabe92440736f7d9e66c47055875401","tid":2450064,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc7a8047e8f24545fc26bf18be02946081899d1","tid":2450064,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cla